{"tid":995670,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"投訢觀塘瑞和街室內運動場, 請大家評理。","createTime":"2019-01-25T15:29:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-25T15:52:39.000Z","uid":38189,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"77c3ffc0dfc90cf9d3cf4e8e2c9469b3dbec0061","tid":995670,"uid":38189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T15:29:11.000Z","msg":"本人發覺好難在平日夜晚在觀塘瑞和街室內運動場book 羽毛球場.<br />\n最近得知, 原來有一間公司, 每逢星期2, 4, 7pm-9pm 都包在個場 (是用團體名義book)<br />\n星期2 打排球, 星期4 打籃球. 人數也不多. 此場得四個場, 都被這間公司估用了.<br />\n我覺得公共設施, 變成私人機構俱樂部, 實在不滿....<br />\n已經作出電話投訴, 都是不是很有作用.<br />\n點解當局能容許一間公司一星期book兩日而且是2小時場?<br />\n如果再有其它公司book, 那麼就不知點算了.<br />\n而且, 星期1, 3, 5都有些球會book了.<br />\n那麼作為普通市民, 想book場打波, 真係好難.<br />\n<img src=\"https://n2-hk.cdn.ampproject.org/i/s/n2.hk/d/images/smilies/default/smile_42.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fn2-hk.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fi%2Fs%2Fn2.hk%2Fd%2Fimages%2Fsmilies%2Fdefault%2Fsmile_42.gif&h=67b5e399&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"556e2476c1a4cc4a33b739f5eba52613a8f8f082","tid":995670,"uid":63864,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T15:32:00.000Z","msg":"我都諗唔明，真係想book都難"},{"pid":"401aa155216b748d57b68586bd256e4d5d10756c","tid":995670,"uid":171754,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T15:33:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7093755206f94ce4ff025ffd9729fceb49f17307","tid":995670,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"401aa155216b748d57b68586bd256e4d5d10756c","tid":995670,"uid":171754,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T15:33:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T15:37:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 未到都針X死你啦"},{"pid":"bd593ba4277590a8cba9923717943be4df1f9a78","tid":995670,"uid":52571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"scor